OL,3,CTrain managers to strike for second
OL,4,Ctime in dispute over rest-day working
OL,6,FPassengers on busy rail routes will
OL,7,Fsuffer fresh disruption on Thursday
OL,8,Fbecause of another strike by train
OL,9,Fmanagers.
OL,11,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,12,FTransport union (RMT) at Avanti West
OL,13,FCoast will walk out for the second
OL,14,Ftime this week in a dispute over rest-
OL,15,Fday working.
OL,17,FThe intercity operator will run one
OL,18,Ftrain an hour between Euston and each
OL,19,Fof Wolverhampton (via Birmingham),
OL,20,FCrewe and Manchester on Thursday.
