OL,6,FThere will also be a limited service
OL,7,Fbetween Glasgow and Preston.
OL,9,FThese trains will operate during
OL,10,Flimited hours ` with the first train
OL,11,Fof the day leaving Euston around 8am
OL,12,Fand the last train of the day from
OL,13,FEuston departing before 5pm.
OL,15,FThe greatly reduced timetables will
OL,16,Fmean North Wales, Blackpool and
OL,17,FEdinburgh have no Avanti West Coast
OL,18,Fservices.
