OL,6,FAvanti said passengers who do travel
OL,7,Fshould plan ahead, expect disruption
OL,8,Fand check the details of their last
OL,9,Ftrain home.
OL,11,FRMT members who work as train managers
OL,12,Fat Avanti West Coast will also be
OL,13,Fstriking every Sunday from 12 January
OL,14,Funtil 25 May 2025.
