OL,3,CTrain managers to strike for second
OL,4,Ctime in dispute over rest-day working
OL,6,FAn RMT spokesperson said: "It is
OL,7,Fwholly unacceptable that replacement
OL,8,Fmanagers can be paid around #500 per
OL,9,Fshift, about double what our Avanti
OL,10,Fmembers earn`while not providing the
OL,11,Fsame service for passengers.
OL,13,F"This kind of destructive approach has
OL,14,Fbeen seen time and again across train
OL,15,Foperating companies and is a hangover
OL,16,Ffrom the previous Conservative
OL,17,Fgovernment, which encouraged practices
OL,18,Fthat reward managers with excessive
OL,19,Fpayouts instead of resolving disputes.
