OL,6,F"Reaching a fair settlement would be
OL,7,Fmore cost-effective and make far
OL,8,Fbetter use of Avanti's resources.
OL,10,F"At the heart of the problem is a
OL,11,Fserious staff shortage, which is why
OL,12,Fthere's such a heavy reliance on
OL,13,Fovertime in the first place."
